  "title": "JOINT RESOLUTION APPROVE AND PUBLISH AND SUBMIT TO THE ELECTORS A PROPOSITION OF AMENDMENT TO THE CONSTITUTION -- OF QUALIFICATION FOR OFFICE",
  "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"upper\"}",
  "classification": [
